T02TD3187E:200b-5: kha dog dmar po rab 'bar 'od zer phung po can //
T02TD3187E:200b-6: 'jam pa'i rdo rje'i sku ni cho ga bzhin bskyed de ;
T02TD3187E:200b-7: / dbyangs yig bcu drug po ni yang dag rdzogs pa las //
T02TD3187E:200b-8: snying gi padma'i dbus su rdo rje legs par bsam //
T02TD3187E:200b-9: me tog bandhu ka yi kha dog dang mtshungs gzugs //
T02TD3187E:200b-10: nges par dmigs bya rkang drug pa zhes grags gyur pa //
T02TD3187E:200b-11: dbugs 'byung rlung dag gis ni dal gyis ma lus par //
T02TD3187E:200b-12: rgyu bar byed cing gnyid kyang sad pa nyid byas nas //
T02TD3187E:200b-13: bsgrub bya mdun na gnas pa legs par bsam bya zhing //
T02TD3187E:200b-14: thal sbyar mig gnyis la ni bung ba'i sgra bsgrags nas //
T02TD3187E:200b-15: bung ba de ni sna sgo gnyis kyi bu ga las //
T02TD3187E:200b-16: bsgrub bya skal ldan snying la rnam par 'jug pa yin //
T02TD3187E:200b-17: dbang du byed pa'i 'jam dpal gyi sgrub thabs so /
T02TD3187E:200b-19: // / aa bha ya las dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
